            <div class="summary-section">
                <h2>üéØ Key Takeaways</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Databases are organized systems for storing and retrieving data</li>
                    <li>They solve problems of data organization, speed, and relationships</li>
                    <li>SQL databases use tables, rows, and columns</li>
                    <li>Every website needs a database to store dynamic content</li>
